members.description: The Royale Compiler will inject html into the index.html file.  Surround with \"inject_html\" tag as follows:  <inject_html> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"http://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.2/themes/smoothness/jquery-ui.css\" /> <script src=\"http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.9.1.js\"></script> <script src=\"http://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.2/jquery-ui.js\"></script> </inject_html>
